      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "You will perhaps recall being advised at the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "time of your visit to this Bureau that the matter discussed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "was not within the jurisdiction of the FBI. However, in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
